'''NGC 1798'''，又記作'''OCL 410'''，是[[御夫座|御夫座]]的[[疏散星团|疏散星团]]，由[[愛德華·愛默生·巴納德|愛德華·巴納德]]於1885年發現。後來[[約翰·德雷耳|約翰·德雷耳]]將其收入原版[[NGC天體表|天體新總表]]（{{lang|en|NGC}}），形容為「一小團恆星，或有星雲狀物」。<ref name=":0222222">{{Cite web|language=en|url=http://cseligman.com/text/atlas/ngc17a.htm#1798|title=New General Catalog Objects: NGC 1750 - 1799|last=Seligman|first=Courtney|website=cseligman.com|date=|publisher=|access-date=2022-03-11|archive-date=2018-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181013181508/http://cseligman.com/text/atlas/ngc17a.htm#1798}}</ref>

星團的直徑為10.2 [[秒差距|pc]]，年齡14億年，[[金屬量|金屬豐度]]為太陽的72 %。其[[徑向速度|徑向速度]]近乎零，[[色指數|''E'' (''B'' −''V'')值]]約為0.51，[[赫羅圖|赫羅圖]]沒有明確的[[紅巨星分支|紅巨星分支]]，沿該分支的星數較少，但在[[紅群聚|紅群聚]]處較多。<ref>{{cite journal|url =http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1999astro.ph..1140P|first1 =Hong Soo|last1= Park|first2 = Myung Gyoon |last2 = Lee|title =UBVI CCD photometry of two old open clusters NGC 1798 and NGC 2192|date =1999-01-01|journal = Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society|volume = 304|issue = 4|pages = 883–892|arxiv = astro-ph/9901140|language = en}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |url =http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2012A%26A...544A.109C|first=R.|last = Carrera|title =Radial velocities and metallicities from infrared Ca II triplet spectroscopy of open clusters . Berkeley 26, Berkeley 70, NGC 1798, and NGC 2266|date =2012-08-01|journal =Astronomy and Astrophysics|volume =544|page =A109|issn=0004-6361|doi=10.1051/0004-6361/201219625|language = en}}</ref>

